messages.message:
FYI you may see a new tool named testmo in your OKTA home page, please click through so your user can be provisioned, this is a tool we will use to help managing our UAT and automated test result history for test analysis and triage failures soon.

For now and 23.01 release you don't need to do anything except clicking the button in OKTA and have your user provisioned, we are still in the process of setting it up, you can ignore any other notifications from testmo. And we will make another announcement when it is ready to be used (ETA 23.02 release)

please feel free to let me know if you run into any errors during user provision. Thanks
